Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:09.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{blur3\fad(100,100)}心烦意乱　隐隐作痛　这一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{blur3\fad(100,100)}这一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:29.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}在你身旁　就苦闷不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:33.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}不住发出叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:40.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}能不能告诉我　你喜欢去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:43.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}顺便请问　你喜欢什么类型呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:50.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}任谁也无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:58.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}无可奈何　这就是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:02.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}早上醒来　就想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:07.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}糟糕的日子里　也爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:13.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}就算见不到面　也还惦记你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:18.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}到了下辈子　也还是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:23.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}Darlin', make me happy lalala I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(100,100)}Darlin', make me happy lalala I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道解除项圈的方法了吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真适合你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.59,0:23:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的魔力 就在雪拉的体内！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚布罗 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊！
